These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, australian, turkish
1. the turkish is on the left of the australian##1
2. the turkish is between the pakistani and the australian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Nationality   | pakistani | turkish | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, scientific, action
1. the person watching crime movies is between the person watching scientific movies and the person watching action movies##2
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | action | crime | scientific |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, country, r&b
1. the fan of country is between the fan of salsa and the fan of r&b##2
2. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | country | salsa |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, bird
1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
2. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the chinchilla##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Pet   | chinchilla | bird | fish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking sprite##2
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Beverage   | sprite | 7up | hot-chocolate |

 #################################

 
